### Proposed Resolution: Expand Scenario 6 to include: GDPR breach assessment checklist (is it reportable?), supervisory authority notification template (varies by country), data subject notification template, ROPA update procedure, and legal counsel escalation trigger criteria.
### Cross-Phase Impact: Phase 4 (Secure) addresses GDPR compliance during build. Phase 6 disaster_recovery must address GDPR incident response at handoff. Without this, Phase 7 maintenance has no compliant breach response protocol.

