### Proposed Resolution: Execute in priority order. P0 items should be built before any new Phase 6 handoffs are executed on production projects. P1 items should be built in parallel with P0 items where possible (sla_handoff and monitoring_handoff are independent of knowledge_audit).
### Cross-Phase Impact: P0 gaps (knowledge_audit, access_handoff, support_enablement, operational_readiness_review) affect every project that uses this framework. The framework currently produces software that is well-built but poorly handed off. These gaps transform Phase 6 from a documentation phase into a true operational transfer phase.
